caption.title: Retraction dynamics and expansion of the distribution area of Ceratophrys cornuta, according to the niche modeling method.
caption.p: Last interglacial (A); Last glacial maximum (B) and Current (C). (A): 59,979 km 2; (B): 166,127 km 2 and (C): 76,329 km 2. Training data: AUC = 0.962 (A); AUC = 0.936 (B) and AUC = 0.956 (C). Test data: AUC = 0.892 (A); AUC = 0.919 (B) and AUC = 0.929.
